---
import Actions from './Actions.astro';
import Cards from './Cards.astro';
---

<section>
  <h2>Fee Information</h2>
  <p>$20 Farewell Fee which includes yearbook, lunch, swag bag and all farewell day activities. You can also include an optional donation towards the Legacy gift.</p>
  <Actions actions={[
    { label: "Pay Fee", href: "https://ecole-westgate-school-parents-society.square.site/" },
  ]} />
  <p><em>If the required fee is a barrier to your student's participation, please reach out to Mme Julie at <a href="mailto:jamuhlberger@cbe.ab.ca">jamuhlberger@cbe.ab.ca</a>. All students will be included in the Farewell Day event.</em></p>

  <Cards>
    <details class="card">
      <summary><h3>Legacy Gift</h3></summary>
      <div class="card-reveal">
        <div class="card-content">
        <p>A Legacy Gift is a special contribution from the graduating Grade 6 class that leaves a lasting mark on the school. Each year, students choose a meaningful gift that future students can enjoy.</p>
        <p>This year, the Grade 6 students will be working with local artist, Sabine Lecorre-Moore, on a special art installation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="card">
      <summary><h3>Volunteering</h3></summary>
      <div class="card-reveal">
        <div class="card-content">
        <p>We have a number of opportunities for parents and guardians to support our Grade 6 Farewell Day activities through volunteering. <a href="https://signup.com/go/jWzdNoQ">Sign up here</a> to help make the day fun, organized, and memorable for our students, and we greatly appreciate your support.</p>
        <p>Thank you for helping us celebrate our Grade 6 students!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>
  </Cards>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: "Bevan", serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin: 0;
  }

  p {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
</style>